msgid "Base class for all non built-in types."
msgstr "所有非内置类型的基类。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:19
msgid "Every class which is not a built-in type inherits from this class."
msgstr "每个不是内置类型的类，都将从该类继承。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:21
msgid ""
"You can construct Objects from scripting languages, using "
"``Object.new()`` in GDScript, ``new Object`` in C#, or the \"Construct "
"Object\" node in VisualScript."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用，GDScript中的 ``Object.new()``、C#中的 ``new Object``、或VisualScript中的 "
"``构造对象（Construct Object）`` 节点，从脚本语言构造对象。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:23
msgid ""
"Objects do not manage memory. If a class inherits from Object, you will "
"have to delete instances of it manually. To do so, call the :ref:`free "
"<class_Object_method_free>` method from your script or delete the "
"instance from C++."
msgstr ""
"``Object`` 不管理内存。如果类继承自 ``Object``，则必须手动删除其实例。为此，请从脚本中调用 :ref:`free "
"<class_Object_method_free>` 方法、或从C++中删除实例。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:25
msgid ""
"Some classes that extend Object add memory management. This is the case "
"of :ref:`Reference <class_Reference>`, which counts references and "
"deletes itself automatically when no longer referenced. :ref:`Node "
"<class_Node>`, another fundamental type, deletes all its children when "
"freed from memory."
msgstr ""
"一些扩展 ``Object`` 的类增加了内存管理。:ref:`Reference <class_Reference>` "
"就是这种情况，它对引用计数，并在不再引用时自动删除自身。:ref:`Node <class_Node>` "
"是另一种基本类型，当从内存中释放时，会删除其所有子级。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:27
msgid ""
"Objects export properties, which are mainly useful for storage and "
"editing, but not really so much in programming. Properties are exported "
"in :ref:`_get_property_list <class_Object_method__get_property_list>` and"
" handled in :ref:`_get <class_Object_method__get>` and :ref:`_set "
"<class_Object_method__set>`. However, scripting languages and C++ have "
"simpler means to export them."
msgstr ""
"``Object`` 导出属性，主要用于存储和编辑，但在编程中并没有那么多。属性在 :ref:`_get_property_list "
"<class_Object_method__get_property_list>` 中导出，并在 :ref:`_get "
"<class_Object_method__get>` 和 :ref:`_set <class_Object_method__set>` "
"中处理。但是，脚本语言和C++具有更简单的导出方法。"

