#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:37
msgid ""
"Objects also receive notifications. Notifications are a simple way to "
"notify the object about different events, so they can all be handled "
"together. See :ref:`_notification <class_Object_method__notification>`."
msgstr ""
"``Object`` 也接收通知。通知是通知对象有关不同事件的一种简单方法，因此它们可以一起处理。参见 :ref:`_notification "
"<class_Object_method__notification>`。"

