#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:160
msgid ""
"**CONNECT_DEFERRED** = **1** --- Connects a signal in deferred mode. This"
" way, signal emissions are stored in a queue, then set on idle time."
msgstr "**CONNECT_DEFERRED** = **1** —— 在延迟模式下连接信号。这样，信号发射被存储在队列中，然后在空闲时间设置。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:162
msgid ""
"**CONNECT_PERSIST** = **2** --- Persisting connections are saved when the"
" object is serialized to file."
msgstr "**CONNECT_PERSIST** = **2** —— 将对象序列化为文件时，将保存持久化连接。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:164
msgid ""
"**CONNECT_ONESHOT** = **4** --- One-shot connections disconnect "
"themselves after emission."
msgstr "**CONNECT_ONESHOT** = **4** —— 单次连接在发射后会自行断开。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:166
msgid ""
"**CONNECT_REFERENCE_COUNTED** = **8** --- Connect a signal as reference "
"counted. This means that a given signal can be connected several times to"
" the same target, and will only be fully disconnected once no references "
"are left."
msgstr ""
"**CONNECT_REFERENCE_COUNTED** = **8** —— "
"连接一个信号作为参考计数。这意味着一个给定的信号可以多次连接到同一目标，并且只有在没有引用的情况下才会完全断开。"

