"将一个 ``signal`` 连接到一个 ``target`` 对象上的一个 ``method``。将可选的 ``binds`` 作为参数的 "
":ref:`Array <class_Array>` 传递给调用。这些参数将在任何参数在调用 :ref:`emit_signal "
"<class_Object_method_emit_signal>` 的方法中使用之后传递给方法。使用 ``flags`` "
"设置延迟或一次性连接。请参阅 :ref:`ConnectFlags <enum_Object_ConnectFlags>` 常量。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:300
msgid ""
"A ``signal`` can only be connected once to a ``method``. It will throw an"
" error if already connected, unless the signal was connected with "
":ref:`CONNECT_REFERENCE_COUNTED "
"<class_Object_constant_CONNECT_REFERENCE_COUNTED>`. To avoid this, first,"
" use :ref:`is_connected <class_Object_method_is_connected>` to check for "
"existing connections."
msgstr ""
"一个 ``signal`` 只能连接到一个 ``method`` 一次。如果已经连接，它将抛出一个错误，除非该信号与 "
":ref:`CONNECT_REFERENCE_COUNTED "
"<class_Object_constant_CONNECT_REFERENCE_COUNTED>` 连接。为了避免这种情况，首先，使用 "
":ref:`is_connected <class_Object_method_is_connected>` 检查现有连接。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_object.rst:302
msgid ""
